  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="AN185.1-kilavi">piriviṭai vēṟupaṭṭa talaimaka ṭōḻikkuc colliyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">What SHE who had undergone changes in the time of separation said to the confidante.</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AN185.1">
        <l>elvaḷai ñekiḻac cāa yāyiḻai</l>
        <l>nalleḻiṟ paṇaittō ḷiruṅkavi ṉaḻiyap</l>
        <l>peruṅkai yaṟṟa neñcamoṭu <supplied>nat</supplied>tuṟa<supplied>n</supplied></l>
        <l>tirumpi ṉiṉṉuyi ruṭaiyōr pōla</l>
        <l>valituval liṉarē kātalar vāṭa</l>
        <l>lolikaḻai nivanta nelluṭai neṭuvetir</l>
        <l>kalikoṇ maḷḷar vilvicaiyi ṉuṭaiyap</l>
        <l>paitaṟa vempiya kalporu parappiṉ</l>
        <l>vēṉi lattat tāṅkaṇ vāṉulan</l>
        <l>taruvi yāṉṟa vuyarcimai maruṅkiṟ</l>
        <l>peruvi<supplied>ḻā</supplied> viḷakkam pōlap palavu<supplied>ṭa</supplied></l>
        <l>ṉilaiyila malarnta vilavamoṭu</l>
        <l>nilaiyuyar piṟaṅkaṉ malaiyi<supplied>ṟa</supplied>n tōrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Abandoning us, with a heart that is greatly desolate (3)</l>
        <l>so that, being emaciated so that [our] bright bangles become loose, the great beauty</l> 
        <l>of [our] fine graceful bamboo shoulders with choice ornaments perishes, (1f.)</l>
        <l>like those who have a soul(?) of iron (4)</l>
        <l>he is very hard, [our] lover, (5a-c)</l>
        <l>– who has gone to traverse the glistening mountains that stand high (13)</l>
        <l>with silk-cotton trees that bloomed without leaves, (12)</l>
        <l>many together, like the lamps of a big festival, (11)</l>
        <l>on high peaks where the waterfalls have ceased (10)</l>
        <l>as the clouds died in that place on the road in summer, (9)</l>
        <l>with surfaces fighting against stones that are heated up so that what is fresh ceases, (8)</l>
        <l>so that the paddy-possessing tall bamboo that has come up with fading noisy stalks (6)</l>
        <l>breaks like the speed of the bows of bustling warriors. (7)</l>
      </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
